article_title: Former Rochester police chief among finalists for Chicago police chief
article_text:
March 17, 2016 11:22 AM

A former Rochester police chief is among the finalists to become the next police chief in Chicago.

The candidates include two African Americans and a retired Washington state police chief who would become the first woman to lead the force.
